                        </div>
                        <div class="col border border-light">
                            <h5 style="color: rgb(240, 190, 100)">PROCESSOR:</h5>
                            <p>Intel Core 2 Duo @2.4 GHz or AMD Athlon X2 @ 2.8 GHZ</p>
